**Professional Profile**
Nguyễn Hoàng Sang is an aspiring professional in the information technology sector, currently pursuing a Software Engineering degree. With 3 months of hands-on experience as an ERP Programmer Intern, Sang gained practical expertise in Oracle ERP systems, including Inventory Management, Accounts Payable, and Order Management modules. Sang is also proficient in utilizing Oracle reporting tools such as BI Publisher and XML Publisher.

**Core Skills & Technology**
Key technical proficiencies include Javascript, Java, Typescript, NestJs, ReactJs, NextJs, MongoDB, PostgreSQL, Git, and RESTful API.

**Education & Certifications**
Nguyễn Hoàng Sang is currently pursuing a Software Engineering degree at Ton Duc Thang University, expected to graduate in 2025. Additionally, Sang holds an Agile-Scrum certificate and a Preliminary English Test (B1) certification.